376
00:18:03.331 --> 00:18:04.832
Scusa.

377
00:18:07.418 --> 00:18:09.295
Grazie.

378
00:18:09.337 --> 00:18:10.796
Dottor Bennell.

379
00:18:10.838 --> 00:18:14.383
Jack Belicec vuole che
vada a casa sua immediatamente.


380
00:18:14.425 --> 00:18:16.260
